      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 18 article about play Designated Mourner, whose American premiere was at Steppenwolf Theater in Chicago in March 1997 (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on June 18 about the play ''The Designated Mourner'' referred to the recent New York production incorrectly. It was not the play's American premiere; that took place at the Steppenwolf Theater in Chicago in March 1997.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
